title: Some issues with reading faces
body:
## Expected behavior

Reading faces from video.

## Actual behavior

Functions "Video A,B , Images A,b" works, Faces A, B didnt work so MODEL ,SWAPS and MOVIE dont work too

## Steps to reproduce

This code is showing
